metadata.name: Unleash the real you
metadata.description:
This is a mask reflecting social anomalies. Societies love to hide beneath these masks. Since the masks are representative of fake personalities, there is no need to talk about people wearing them anymore. They replace the wrinkled face and all the bad personality traits. As if they were like the screens which deceive us. Please unleash the masks.
Ink in combination with colored pencil on paper.
3068*3449
